00:28.320 --> 00:34.640
and how they interact. There are four main components of a VQE calculation.

6
00:34.640 --> 00:40.879
First, there's an operator, often a Hamiltonian, which we'll call H, that describes a property of the system that

7
00:40.879 --> 00:47.280
