01:02.320 --> 01:09.360
the igen vector you're seeking. Really, the Anzots is a family of quantum circuits because some of the gates in

11
01:09.360 --> 01:18.159
the Anzots are parameterized. That is, they are fed a parameter which we can vary. This family of quantum circuits

