04:23.120 --> 04:26.320
to tailor our guess as much as possible.

39
04:26.320 --> 04:33.120
Second, we would calculate the expectation value of the operator with the system in that state.

40
04:33.120 --> 04:37.360
Third, we would alter the variational parameters and repeat.

41
04:37.360 --> 04:45.360
Fourth, we would use accumulated information about the landscape of possible states in your variational subspace to make better and better

